OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussian threat means UK    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Farmy needs more cash, says 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FBen Wallace                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Defence Secretary Ben Wallace is urging
OL,6, the prime minister to increase spending
OL,7, on the UK's armed forces in light of   
OL,8, Russia's invasion of Ukraine.          
OL,10,FHe already successfully pushed for     
OL,11,Fhigher spending in 2020, but will say  
OL,12,Fin a speech later that the threat has  
OL,13,Fnow changed.                           
OL,15,FThe UK currently spends around 2% of   
OL,16,Fits GDP on defence, matching the target
OL,17,FNato sets for its members.             
OL,19,FBut Mr Wallace is expected to ask the  
OL,20,FPM to increase that to 2.5% by 2028.   
